a:5:{s:5:"title";s:59:"Method CRM: Jobs “New Customer” now opens in a pop-up";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:437:"<p>Method CRM changed the Jobs workflow so “New Customer” opens the creation screen in a modal pop-up.<br />
